thor-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-wwxs7iJe3IRK6mSsXfh_gQ">Thảo đường - 草堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%87nh/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-BK7d1VsxQyz8Rjk9o6kE3Q">Thu dạ - 秋夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%87nh/author-Wi4-g6g_EJiYCavfRigKbw">Vương Lệnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/V%C4%83n-nh%C6%B0-Si%C3%AAu-Qu%C3%A1t-v%C3%B4-Ti%E1%BB%81n-H%C3%A1n/poem-F06gMIt6uyNXFY__CJ3oEw">Văn như Siêu, Quát vô Tiền Hán - 文如超适無前暵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/author-1olZ3UNbr3C-_4X52NnUtA">Tự Đức hoàng đế</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/V%C5%A9-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%B9ng-Phong-c%C3%A1c/poem--RZ9Jn4HmCKliMa4SEQc0g">Vũ Xương Tùng Phong các - 武昌松風閣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/author-wRpSKwqTcKjFpinJIe2YPg">Hoàng Đình Kiên</a>)<br></div>	</div>
